What is the RHEA ID for the reaction corresponding to EC number uniprot_enzyme:7.1.3.1
sparql:
# Endpoint: https://sparql.rhea-db.org/sparql
# Description: What is the RHEA ID for the reaction corresponding to EC number uniprot_enzyme:7.1.3.1
# Parameter: reaction_ec_number: (example: uniprot_enzyme:7.1.3.1)

PREFIX rhea: <http://rdf.rhea-db.org/>
PREFIX uniprot_enzyme: <http://purl.uniprot.org/enzyme/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?Reaction 
WHERE {
    VALUES ?reaction_ec_number { uniprot_enzyme:7.1.3.1 }
    ?Reaction rhea:ec ?reaction_ec_number .
}
LIMIT 100
